            ^"Duration" STRING "Concentration, up to 1 minute"
            ^"Concentration" BOOLEAN true
            ^"Description" STRING "You bless up to three creatures of your choice within range. Whenever a target makes an attack roll or a saving throw before the spell ends, the target can roll a d4 and add the number rolled to the attack roll or saving throw."
            ^"At Higher Levels" STRING "When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, you can target one additional creature for each slot level above 1st."
            ^"Classes" LIST OF STRING ["Cleric", "Paladin"]
