            ^"Description" STRING "You touch a willing creature who isn’t wearing armor, and a protective magical force surrounds it until the spell ends. The target’s base AC becomes 13 + its Dexterity modifier. The spell ends if the target dons armor or if you dismiss the spell as an action."
            ^"Classes" LIST OF STRING ["Sorcerer", "Wizard"]
