                        ^"PEX Cost"
                        INTEGER 50
                        ^"Description"
                        STRING "The antiquarian knows how to identify the value of art objects and historical objects even though they are not magical in nature. The antiquarian gains advantage on Intelligence rolls made for appraisal. Also, the antiquarian receives 10% more gold while selling the items he acquired."
