                        STRING "Each specialty gets different use of this innovation:

Historian: The Historian gains the ability to use locate object and tongues once a day. This ability is refreshed at a short or long rest.

Arcanist: The Arcanist gains the ability to use augury and clairvoyance once a day. This ability is refreshed at a short or long rest."
