                STRING "(5000 PEX)"
                PERKS {
                    #tGDnB7t6B8QjjIObM9rjxGRI ^"Stories of the Past:" DEF {
                        EXTENDS ^"Profession Perk"
                        ^"PEX Cost"
                        INTEGER 0
                        ^"Description"
                        STRING "You have a lot of experiences, stories, and have probably taken part in some of the legends and myths. You have the ability to inspire greatness in others. You can grant inspiration to anyone who listens to your stories a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus daily. This inspiration point must be used in 1 hour or it will be lost. Anyone who already has an inspiration point won't be affected by this."
