            }
            #tLqLekg0kDXStrVVv7vcBjrh ^"Omens from the Sky (4/day)" DEF {
                EXTENDS ^"Stat Block Feature"
                ^"Category"
                STRING "Trait"
                ^"Description"
                STRING "The muneccim bashi can touch a creature to grant them one of the abilities below, that is active for 1 minute. Once used, the ability is lost. A creature can’t have more than one benefit active on them at the same time. The muneccim can regain a use of it by expending a spell slot (action required)
Bad Omen: When the creature is hit by an attack, it can use its reaction to roll a d10 and deduct it from the roll, potentially causing it to miss. Good Omen: When the creature misses an attack roll, it can use its reaction to roll a d10 and add it to their attack roll, potentially causing it to hit."
            }
