                EXTENDS ^"Stat Block Feature"
                ^"Category"
                STRING "Trait"
                ^"Description"
                STRING "As a reaction the naziat will activate its dread aura. Any evil creature in a 10 ft. area will take 3 (1d6) radiant damage for each turn spent in the area and it can’t regain hit points while they are still in this area. This aura persists for one minute and the Naziat will regain its use when it performs a short rest."
